There are forty-four...

322
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:24,240
There are...

323
00:14:25,570 --> 00:14:26,700
(Tongue tied)

324
00:14:28,530 --> 00:14:29,540
(Again)

325
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:31,780
There are forty-four.

326
00:14:31,950 --> 00:14:34,550
There are forty-four.

327
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:38,060
(Trying super hard)
Astringent persimmon trees.

328
00:14:38,350 --> 00:14:38,970
Astringent...

329
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:41,340
It's a tongue twister.

330
00:14:42,890 --> 00:14:44,630
Are you ready?
Who wants to challenge first?

331
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:46,080
