Our youth! Our destiny for eternity)

371
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:12,490
(Happy to see everyone)

372
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:16,560
Seven, right, four,
two, three, four, five.

373
00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:18,960
