382
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:44,830
(Rikimaru checking in on their progress)
Hello, teacher.

383
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:45,870
(Rikimaru checking in on their progress)
Hello.

384
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:47,140
Hello, teacher.

385
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:47,870
Hi.

386
