393
00:18:06,780 --> 00:18:10,090
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

394
00:18:10,090 --> 00:18:10,530
One.

395
00:18:10,530 --> 00:18:11,930
(Formation not aligned)

396
00:18:11,930 --> 00:18:14,410
(Moves not in sync)
Four, five, six, seven, right.

397
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:17,130
(Forgot the moves)

398
00:18:17,580 --> 00:18:19,020
