417
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:54,200
Here.

418
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:57,750
Seven, and go.

419
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:59,330
One, two.

420
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:01,660
Four, and pose.

421
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:02,940
Six, and pose.

422
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:05,360
