464
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,120
We're geniuses.

465
00:20:44,120 --> 00:20:45,720
(Genius)
We're geniuses.

466
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,470
Yes.

467
00:20:49,340 --> 00:20:52,650
