480
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:16,730
You must adjust in a team.

481
00:21:16,730 --> 00:21:18,930
Balance is very important too.

482
00:21:18,930 --> 00:21:21,980
I'm worried about Jony and Leo the most.

483
00:21:21,980 --> 00:21:22,940
(Most worried about Jony and Leo)

484
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:33,770
(Happy
Serious)

485
00:21:34,430 --> 00:21:35,110
I think it looks good.

486
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:36,760
If we match it with the right costumes

487
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:38,000
