One, two, three.

503
00:22:06,860 --> 00:22:07,490
Yes.

504
00:22:07,490 --> 00:22:08,830
No, I did it wrong.

505
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:09,840
Okay.

506
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:11,220
