without permission.

544
00:25:01,690 --> 00:25:03,380
Last night, someone left
without permission.

545
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:09,380
Jony went out
from 9 p.m. to 2 a.m. last night

546
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:10,180
