1210
00:59:29,950 --> 00:59:31,930
I'm really grateful he brought me here.

1211
00:59:31,930 --> 00:59:33,720
We definitely splurged tonight.

1212
00:59:33,720 --> 00:59:35,030
Let's look forward to

1213
00:59:35,030 --> 00:59:38,140
